1
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:18,500
Regarding Jiu, don't worry.

2
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:21,500
The poison of orchid will slowly get into the blood

3
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:22,500
Eventually he coughs up blood and dies.

4
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,500
And where is he?

5
00:00:25,100 --> 00:00:27,500
Jiu... Jiu is dead.

6
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:31,500
Even if I announce the marriage,

7
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:35,500
he will know one day that you have poison that is used to kill people.

8
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:37,500
what are you going to do?

9
00:00:37,800 --> 00:00:41,500
Jia and I have already thought about how it should end.

10
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:43,500
I have a solution.

11
00:00:44,500 --> 00:00:46,500
Tomorrow before the ceremony starts, we have to stop Mr. Ma.

12
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:49,500
Kill him before he arrives.

13
00:00:49,800 --> 00:00:51,500
Mr. Ma has absolutely no way of exposing Mr. Tian.

14
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:54,500
Li.

15
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:05,500
I love you, Tian.

16
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:09,500
Everything must end today.

17
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:55,500
Before paying respect, fill up with the tea.

18
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:08,500
Wait.

19
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:10,500
Do you see Nuan?

20
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,500
I see her walking towards the back of the house, Sir.

21
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,500
Thanks.

22
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:11,500
What is Mr. Tian doing? Sneak up like that.

23
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:55,500
What did he hide?

24
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:20,500
What? You said Tian hid something?

25
00:05:20,700 --> 00:05:22,500
I don't know what he is hiding. But it's suspicious.

26
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:25,500
It must be something really important.

27
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:33,500
Good, take me there quickly.

28
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,500
Yes, Madam.

29
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:50,500
Let's go, Jia, or we won't be in time.

30
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:12,500
Oh, Sir.

31
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:19,500
Where have you been?

32
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:26,500
We...

33
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:29,500
I feel better now.

34
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:31,500
So I go out for some fresh air.

35
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:45,500
What about the blood on your head?

36
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:48,500
Why do you have a wound?

37
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:51,500
I'm not careful enough,

38
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:54,500
so I walked into the door and hit my head.

39
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:56,500
You were stupid enough to walked into the door?

40
00:06:57,500 --> 00:06:59,500
You think I'm so stupid that I will believe your lie?

41
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:02,500
Tell me now.

42
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:04,500
Where have you been?

43
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:14,500
Are you going to tell me?

44
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:17,500
The blood on your head.

45
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:19,500
Is it your blood or whose blood?

46
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:22,500
Sir.

47
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:25,500
If you want to hurt anyone,

48
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:28,500
do it to me.

49
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:33,500
What evil stuff have you done again, Li?

50
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,120
For you,

51
00:07:39,248 --> 00:07:41,248
it might be evil stuff.

52
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:44,500
But for me,

53
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:48,500
it's what a mother has to do.

54
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:59,500
Father, what is this about?

55
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:16,500
Father.

56
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:19,500
If you have something,

57
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:22,500
put it aside first.

58
00:08:25,500 --> 00:08:26,500
Let's get through today.

59
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:31,500
I beg you.

60
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:41,500
It's almost the time.

61
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:44,500
I think we better go.

62
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:50,500
Please, Father.

63
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:33,500
Where is the thing Tian hiding?

64
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:36,500
I don't know.

65
00:09:37,500 --> 00:09:40,500
What? Why don't you wait to see until he finished hiding?

66
00:09:41,500 --> 00:09:43,500
I was in a hurry to tell you.

67
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:44,500
Bitch.

68
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:47,500
Help find it.

69
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:48,500
Yes, Madam.

70
00:10:11,500 --> 00:10:13,500
Father, let's go.

71
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:15,500
The ceremony is starting soon.

72
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:48,500
Have you found it?

73
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:49,500
No, Madam.

74
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:50,500
Find it.

75
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:53,500
Perhaps this thing will help turn the tide.

76
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:54,500
Alright, Madam.

77
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:04,500
Big Brother.

78
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,500
Chun, Tong.

79
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:11,500
Big brother, are you okay?

80
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:13,500
It seems like you aren't feeling well?

81
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:23,500
It's nothing. Mr. Song must be tired.

82
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:31,500
Should we start the ceremony now?

83
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:34,500
How can we start?

84
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:37,500
Ma and Chan are not here yet.

85
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:39,500
But if we wait, it won't be an auspicious time.

86
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,500
Right, Big Brother.

87
00:11:41,900 --> 00:11:44,500
I think we don't need to wait for Ma.

88
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:48,500
He never follows the rules and never be on time.

89
00:11:49,100 --> 00:11:51,500
If he doesn't see the importance of other people's time,

90
00:11:52,500 --> 00:11:54,500
why do we need to wait for someone like this?

91
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:57,500
I agree with this.

92
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:01,500
So Ma will know that we are not satisfied with him either.

93
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,500
Did you find it?

94
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:18,500
No, Madam.

95
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:22,500
For today's meeting,

96
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:25,500
I have something important to let everyone know.

97
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:27,500
Tian.

98
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:55,500
I want to announce that

99
00:13:57,500 --> 00:14:00,500
I will arrange a wedding for Tian and Mud,

100
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:05,500
and pass the leader title of the Five Dragons Association to him

101
00:14:05,800 --> 00:14:07,500
in the next three days.

102
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:12,500
Would anyone oppose?

103
00:14:13,500 --> 00:14:15,500
Why are you in such a hurry, Big Brother?

104
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:20,500
Hasn't Tian recently broken off the engagement with Lady Pin?

105
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:23,500
Oh, Chun.

106
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:26,500
Young people always like this.

107
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:28,500
Impatient.

108
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:32,500
Lovers can't wait, of course.

109
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:35,500
I think it's good.

110
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,500
After Tian gets married,

111
00:14:37,900 --> 00:14:40,500
you gives the leader title of the Five Dragons Association to him.

112
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:43,500
So Tian can help you take care of your works.

113
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:48,500
Your health isn't quite good lately, is it?

114
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:56,500
Then I won't oppose this.

115
00:14:58,500 --> 00:15:01,500
I think Tian is the most suitable one

116
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:04,500
to inherit the position from you.

117
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:09,500
He is diligent and kind to the workers.

118
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:13,500
From now on, I'll have to call you Mr. Tian as well.

119
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:54,500
Madam, I found it.

120
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:57,500
Come on, let me see it.

121
00:16:08,500 --> 00:16:09,500
This is…

122
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:22,500
If no one opposes,

123
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:25,500
I will arrange a wedding for Tian and Mud,

124
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:29,500
as well as passing the leader title of the Five Dragons Association to him

125
00:16:30,500 --> 00:16:32,500
in the next three days.

126
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:33,500
No, you can't.

127
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:46,500
Mom.

128
00:16:49,500 --> 00:16:54,500
Tian didn't deserve to be the head of the Five Dragons Association.

129
00:16:58,500 --> 00:16:59,500
Can you stop causing trouble?

130
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:00,500
What are you talking about?

131
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:02,500
Right, Chan.

132
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:04,500
Why are you making a mess?

133
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,500
Take her out now.

134
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:09,500
Stop, No. Go away.

135
00:17:10,500 --> 00:17:11,500
Nuan.

136
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:13,500
Tell them what you saw.

137
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:18,500
I saw Mr. Tian sneaking to hide something as if he has a secret.

138
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:21,500
When I followed him, I found this, Sir.

139
00:18:01,500 --> 00:18:02,500
Sleeping powder.

140
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:06,500
What did he hide?

141
00:19:15,500 --> 00:19:16,500
What is that letter?

142
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:18,500
Nuan, give it to me.

143
00:19:19,500 --> 00:19:20,500
Give it to me. / No, Mr. Yang.

144
00:19:20,700 --> 00:19:21,500
Mom.

145
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:23,500
Let me go. / Mr. Yang.

146
00:19:23,700 --> 00:19:24,500
Mom.

147
00:19:24,600 --> 00:19:27,500
This letter was written by Jiu to Tian

148
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:29,500
making an appointment to run away with each other.

149
00:19:30,500 --> 00:19:32,500
It clearly stated that they were lovers.

150
00:19:40,500 --> 00:19:41,500
Nuan, let me go! / Mr. Yang.

151
00:19:42,500 --> 00:19:44,500
Please come to meet me tomorrow.

152
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:47,500
I'll tell you everything

153
00:19:47,700 --> 00:19:49,500
and let's run away together.

154
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:52,500
I love you, Tian.

155
00:19:56,500 --> 00:19:57,500
Chan.

156
00:19:58,500 --> 00:20:00,500
What the hell are you talking about?

157
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:10,500
What is this, Tian?

158
00:20:14,500 --> 00:20:16,500
Tian is a homosexual like Mr. Zhang.

159
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:21,500
How are you going to judge?

160
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:25,500
In the past, Mr. Zhang was exposed that he was a homosexual.

161
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:30,500
You had expelled him from the association until he committed suicide.

162
00:20:31,500 --> 00:20:32,500
How about this time?

163
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:35,500
Are you going to let it go like this?

164
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,500
Are you letting Tian become the head of the association?

165
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:40,500
Shut up, Chan.

166
00:20:40,900 --> 00:20:44,500
You made up the story because you wanted to steal the position for Yang.

167
00:20:45,500 --> 00:20:47,500
No one would believe the lie that you said.

168
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:52,500
What would you say?

169
00:20:55,500 --> 00:20:58,500
Tell me that it's not true.

170
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:01,500
What Chan said was not true, say it.

171
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:09,500
Tian, Tian.

172
00:21:10,100 --> 00:21:10,600
Tell me.

173
00:21:11,500 --> 00:21:12,500
That the whole thing isn't true.

174
00:21:13,500 --> 00:21:14,500
It's all a misunderstanding.

175
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:16,500
Tell everyone.

176
00:21:21,500 --> 00:21:22,500
I'm sorry, father.

177
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:29,500
What Aunt Chan said is true.

178
00:22:03,500 --> 00:22:04,500
I like men.

179
00:22:07,500 --> 00:22:08,500
Tian.

180
00:22:08,700 --> 00:22:10,500
It's the truth that I've been hiding all along.

181
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:13,500
Tian, stop.

182
00:22:13,700 --> 00:22:14,200
Yang.

183
00:22:17,500 --> 00:22:19,500
In the past, I lived in fear.

184
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,500
I'm embarrassed.

185
00:22:24,500 --> 00:22:26,500
It's like I have to lie to everyone all the time.

186
00:22:28,500 --> 00:22:30,500
But when I said it out,

187
00:22:32,500 --> 00:22:34,500
I've never been at ease like this before, Yang.

188
00:22:37,500 --> 00:22:39,500
Tian.

189
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:40,500
Bua,

190
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:43,500
don't be sad.

191
00:22:45,500 --> 00:22:47,500
Don't pity me.

192
00:22:49,500 --> 00:23:00,500
I don't need sympathy
or understanding from everyone.

193
00:23:00,500 --> 00:23:02,500
I just want to be myself.

194
00:23:04,500 --> 00:23:06,500
I want to live my life the way I choose

195
00:23:09,500 --> 00:23:11,500
in which everyone respects me.

196
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:14,500
Not too much.

197
00:23:15,500 --> 00:23:16,500
Not too less.

198
00:23:19,500 --> 00:23:22,500
Just as much as a person deserves.

199
00:23:28,300 --> 00:23:29,300
All these years,

200
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:33,300
I've always tried to hide the fact that I like men.

201
00:23:37,180 --> 00:23:39,180
But Aunt Chan found this letter in the end.

202
00:23:41,180 --> 00:23:42,180
Previously,

203
00:23:43,180 --> 00:23:45,180
our worker, Dong, knew this secret.

204
00:23:46,180 --> 00:23:50,180
So I had to kill him to cover this up.

205
00:23:56,180 --> 00:23:59,180
The tiny box that comes with the letter.

206
00:23:59,180 --> 00:24:00,180
Huh?

207
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:04,180
It's the poison I used to kill Dong.

208
00:24:06,180 --> 00:24:07,180
Does this box contain poison?

209
00:24:11,180 --> 00:24:13,180
Not true, Tian. What did you say?

210
00:24:13,480 --> 00:24:15,180
Why are you lying? Huh?

211
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:18,180
Killing someone to keep secrets. You evil.

212
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:20,180
That's not true. I don't believe it.

213
00:24:20,480 --> 00:24:22,180
Someone like you can't kill people. That's not true.

214
00:24:22,380 --> 00:24:23,180
Yes.

215
00:24:24,180 --> 00:24:25,180
Tian definitely wouldn't do that, Father.

216
00:24:26,180 --> 00:24:27,180
What is this?

217
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:29,180
This isn't true, right?

218
00:24:35,180 --> 00:24:36,180
Father.

219
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:37,180
Sir.

220
00:24:43,180 --> 00:24:44,180
What did you do?

221
00:24:46,180 --> 00:24:47,180
Tian.

222
00:24:50,180 --> 00:24:52,180
You ruined the honor of the Song family

223
00:24:54,180 --> 00:24:55,180
that we have accumulated.

224
00:24:59,180 --> 00:25:01,180
You're ruining our clan.

225
00:25:04,180 --> 00:25:05,180
Father.

226
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:26,180
Father.

227
00:25:30,180 --> 00:25:31,180
I'm sorry

228
00:25:32,180 --> 00:25:36,180
that I couldn't become the son that you and Mother expected me to be.

229
00:25:40,180 --> 00:25:44,180
But this child does the best job.

230
00:25:45,180 --> 00:25:46,180
Are you crazy?

231
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:48,180
What did you do? Did you realize it?

232
00:25:49,180 --> 00:25:51,180
Tell me now that it's not true. It's not true.

233
00:25:52,180 --> 00:25:53,180
Tian.

234
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:56,180
What kind of duty are you doing?

235
00:25:58,180 --> 00:25:59,180
You ungrateful child!

236
00:26:00,180 --> 00:26:01,180
You ungrateful child!

237
00:26:12,180 --> 00:26:13,180
Sir.

238
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:14,180
Father.

239
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,180
Big Brother.

240
00:26:15,380 --> 00:26:16,180
Let go of me.

241
00:26:17,180 --> 00:26:18,180
Father.

242
00:26:18,380 --> 00:26:19,180
Sir.

243
00:26:24,180 --> 00:26:25,180
Sir.

244
00:27:08,180 --> 00:27:10,180
How is Mr. Song, doctor?

245
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:12,180
He's better now.

246
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:13,180
I'll prescribe medicine

247
00:27:14,180 --> 00:27:17,180
but you must be careful not to let anything stress him.

248
00:27:18,180 --> 00:27:19,180
Thanks.

249
00:27:24,180 --> 00:27:25,180
Why are you here?

250
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:26,180
Do you still dare to come in?

251
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:30,180
If you go inside, Mr. Song will be worse after seeing you.

252
00:27:32,180 --> 00:27:33,180
A homosexual

253
00:27:33,480 --> 00:27:35,180
and a killer.

254
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:38,180
You shameless.

255
00:27:39,180 --> 00:27:40,180
Mom.

256
00:28:25,180 --> 00:28:26,180
Tian.

257
00:28:28,180 --> 00:28:29,180
Why are you doing this?

258
00:28:33,180 --> 00:28:35,180
What do you mean?

259
00:28:43,180 --> 00:28:45,180
If you talk about Dong's death,

260
00:28:47,180 --> 00:28:49,180
It's because he knew my secret,

261
00:28:50,180 --> 00:28:51,180
so I had to kill him.

262
00:28:54,180 --> 00:28:55,180
I've told you everything.

263
00:28:57,180 --> 00:28:59,180
You think I'll believe you?

264
00:29:01,180 --> 00:29:03,180
You can lie to others, but not me.

265
00:29:07,180 --> 00:29:08,180
I grew up with you.

266
00:29:09,180 --> 00:29:11,180
I know what are you like.

267
00:29:12,180 --> 00:29:14,180
You can't even kill an ant.

268
00:29:16,180 --> 00:29:18,180
And that letter.

269
00:29:19,180 --> 00:29:22,180
If you wanted to destroy that letter, why didn't you burn it?

270
00:29:24,180 --> 00:29:28,180
You buried it and deliberately let Mom and Nuan see it, right?

271
00:29:36,180 --> 00:29:37,180
Yes.

272
00:29:40,180 --> 00:29:42,180
I want to end everything, Yang.

273
00:29:47,180 --> 00:29:49,180
About my secret

274
00:29:51,180 --> 00:29:53,180
and Dong's death.

275
00:29:56,180 --> 00:29:58,180
Someone must plead guilty.

276
00:30:02,180 --> 00:30:03,180
If I don’t admit it,

277
00:30:06,180 --> 00:30:08,180
Mother must be punished.

278
00:30:10,180 --> 00:30:11,180
Yang.

279
00:30:26,180 --> 00:30:28,180
I've made up my mind, Yang.

280
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:33,180
Could you please

281
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:38,180
take care of Father and Mother for me, okay?

